00:27:53,439 --> 00:27:55,439
I'm not flooding it!
You're over-cranking it.

536
00:27:55,441 --> 00:27:57,441
Oh, you don't know
what you're talking about!

537
00:27:57,443 --> 00:27:59,910
We're still getting paid
whether we get there or not.

538
00:27:59,912 --> 00:28:01,278
Maybe we should
catch the bus.

539
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:02,680
Sh...
Come on!

540
00:28:02,682 --> 00:28:04,815
Just...
It's gonna start, okay?

541
00:28:04,817 --> 00:28:06,917
[Sputtering continues]
Yeah, you definitely
flooded it.

542
00:28:06,919 --> 00:28:08,352
He drained the battery.
You drained the battery.

543
00:28:08,354 --> 00:28:09,787
Can you not
talk about something

544
00:28:09,789 --> 00:28:11,155
you know
absolutely nothing about?

545
00:28:11,157 --> 00:28:12,423
There's a bus
we could get in.

546
00:28:12,425 --> 00:28:13,824
Shh! Shh!

547
00:28:13,826 --> 00:28:15,959
I just need to think
