548
00:28:15,961 --> 00:28:17,461
[Sighs]

549
00:28:17,463 --> 00:28:19,763
Look,
we're taking the bus.

550
00:28:19,765 --> 00:28:21,031
Yeah.

551
00:28:22,033 --> 00:28:24,802
[Grunts]

552
00:28:24,804 --> 00:28:27,171
[Trunk creaks]

553
00:28:28,773 --> 00:28:30,174
[Panting]

554
00:28:30,176 --> 00:28:31,842
