734
00:37:13,298 --> 00:37:14,831
[Groans]

735
00:37:14,833 --> 00:37:16,566
[Sighs]

736
00:37:26,444 --> 00:37:31,414
[Sighs]

737
00:37:33,851 --> 00:37:35,518
[Sighs]

738
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:38,855
[Vehicles passing in distance]

739
00:37:38,857 --> 00:37:41,992
[Chuckles]

740
00:37:41,994 --> 00:37:44,294
Hey,
let's get outta here.

741
00:37:44,296 --> 00:37:46,029
[Scoffs] What?

742
00:37:46,031 --> 00:37:47,597
Get out where?

743
00:37:47,599 --> 00:37:51,301
I am up to my neck
in mesa verde. I can't.

744
00:37:51,303 --> 00:37:51,301
C'mon,
we're going.

745
00:37:51,303 --> 00:37:52,969
No, I can't.
Up.

746
00:37:52,971 --> 00:37:54,371
Jimmy...
Na-ah!

747
00:37:54,373 --> 00:37:55,872
Nope. Nothing...
[Laughs]

748
00:37:55,874 --> 00:37:57,874
Nothing you can do
to stop this.

749
00:37:57,876 --> 00:37:59,309
[Inhales sharply]

750
00:37:59,311 --> 00:38:00,810
Uh, one thing...
You have to drive.

751
00:38:00,812 --> 00:38:02,412
[Kruder & dorfmeister's
<i> "black baby"</i> plays]

752
00:38:02,414 --> 00:38:03,813
Oh, oh, oh.

753
00:38:03,815 --> 00:38:05,915
Lookit this guy.

754
00:38:05,917 --> 00:38:07,417
Ohh.

755
00:38:07,419 --> 00:38:10,553
