in a rented toupee.

756
00:38:10,555 --> 00:38:11,888
[Laughs] C'mon.

757
00:38:11,890 --> 00:38:13,556
Why would you
rent a toupee?

758
00:38:13,558 --> 00:38:15,392
Y'know,
from the toupee store.

759
00:38:15,394 --> 00:38:17,560
So you don't
have to maintain it.

760
00:38:17,562 --> 00:38:19,329
[Chuckles]

761
00:38:19,331 --> 00:38:21,564
All right.
Seven and seven.

762
00:38:21,566 --> 00:38:22,899
Yeah.

763
00:38:22,901 --> 00:38:24,401
And an old fashioned.

764
00:38:24,403 --> 00:38:26,303
Keep 'em coming,
good sir.

765
00:38:26,305 --> 00:38:27,904
Uh, oh.
[Clears throat]

766
00:38:27,906 --> 00:38:30,907
Can you, uh,
start charging this card

767
00:38:30,909 --> 00:38:32,742
instead of
that other one?
Yeah, yeah.
You got it.

768
00:38:32,744 --> 00:38:34,944
Thank you. [Sniffles]
No problem.

769
00:38:34,946 --> 00:38:37,914
