00:38:51,763 --> 00:38:53,630
Look,
is it wrong...

777
00:38:53,632 --> 00:38:55,932
Whoa.
Hey, hey, this guy over here.

778
00:38:55,934 --> 00:38:57,767
[Inhales sharply]

779
00:38:57,769 --> 00:39:01,071
