what a big spender he is.

780
00:39:01,073 --> 00:39:04,441
I got every dollar
the guy owns.

781
00:39:04,443 --> 00:39:06,843
We're here
to meet a celebrity

782
00:39:06,845 --> 00:39:09,412
who's donating
to my charity.

783
00:39:09,414 --> 00:39:10,680
Kevin costner.

784
00:39:10,682 --> 00:39:13,683
I-I will go stand
in that corner.

785
00:39:13,685 --> 00:39:17,787
You point me out...
You're meeting Kevin costner.

786
00:39:17,789 --> 00:39:20,056
What? You don't look like
Kevin costner.

787
00:39:20,058 --> 00:39:22,459
Uh... I look exactly like
Kevin costner.

788
00:39:22,461 --> 00:39:23,693
People are always
coming up to me,

789
00:39:23,695 --> 00:39:25,962
saying they loved me
in "bull durham."

790
00:39:25,964 --> 00:39:27,497
Never.
Never happened.

791
00:39:27,499 --> 00:39:28,798
Always.
No, not once.

792
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:30,467
[Snapping fingers]
Hey! Hey, you!

