839
00:41:06,731 --> 00:41:09,566
♪♪

840
00:41:09,568 --> 00:41:10,900
Nothing.

841
00:41:10,902 --> 00:41:12,802
It's not nothing.

842
00:41:12,804 --> 00:41:17,874
What?
I keep thinking...

843
00:41:17,876 --> 00:41:19,709
Was there
another way?

844
00:41:19,711 --> 00:41:23,079
[Chuckling]
Another way?

845
00:41:23,081 --> 00:41:24,581
W... Chuck?

846
00:41:24,583 --> 00:41:25,882
Is that what
you're talking about?

847
00:41:25,884 --> 00:41:29,819
