856
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:50,273
Woman:
Why, thank you.

857
00:41:50,275 --> 00:41:53,877
Have a good evening.

858
00:41:53,879 --> 00:41:55,612
[Sighs]

859
00:41:55,614 --> 00:42:01,618
[Indistinct conversations,
