Claire's land in South Africa.

866
00:42:22,641 --> 00:42:23,973
Oh, yeah.

867
00:42:23,975 --> 00:42:25,275
Definitely.

868
00:42:25,277 --> 00:42:26,743
[Sighs]

869
00:42:26,745 --> 00:42:30,146
The mining rights
