874
00:42:43,995 --> 00:42:47,263
[Keys jingle]

875
00:42:47,265 --> 00:42:50,800
[Wind whistling]

876
00:43:00,344 --> 00:43:04,347
[Sighs]

877
00:43:04,349 --> 00:43:05,782
Really?

878
00:43:05,784 --> 00:43:07,750
He called me.

879
00:43:07,752 --> 00:43:09,118
For obvious reasons.

880
00:43:09,120 --> 00:43:11,754
Look, I'm not here
to rip him off.

881
00:43:11,756 --> 00:43:13,723
He has the stuff,
right?

882
