not to do this?

900
00:43:56,635 --> 00:43:58,267
I'm not
tellin' you anything.

901
00:43:58,269 --> 00:44:01,371
Just want to make sure you know
what you're getting into.

902
00:44:01,373 --> 00:44:03,239
I'm not
getting into anything.

903
00:44:03,241 --> 00:44:04,741
I'm in it.

904
00:44:04,743 --> 00:44:06,976
I've got no choice.

905
00:44:10,414 --> 00:44:11,914
[Sighs]

906
00:44:11,916 --> 00:44:13,650
