is a straight arrow.

908
00:44:15,020 --> 00:44:16,252
He won't
stand for it,

909
00:44:16,254 --> 00:44:18,254
which means
he goes to the police,

910
00:44:18,256 --> 00:44:21,391
which means
he's a dead man.

911
00:44:21,393 --> 00:44:24,060
And that's not happening.

912
00:44:24,062 --> 00:44:27,096
You get caught,
it could get worse.

913
00:44:27,098 --> 00:44:28,931
You don't think
I know who I'm dealing with?

914
00:44:28,933 --> 00:44:30,233
No.

915
00:44:30,235 --> 00:44:32,335
I don't.

916
00:44:48,919 --> 00:44:50,753
[Gas cap rattling]

917
00:44:50,755 --> 00:44:52,722
What are you doing?

918
00:45:05,002 --> 00:45:07,470
[Gas cap rattling]

919
00:45:07,472 --> 00:45:09,806
[Gas-cap door closes]

920
00:45:12,810 --> 00:45:14,977
There are more people
than the salamancas

921
00:45:14,979 --> 00:45:16,379
to worry about here.

922
00:45:16,381 --> 00:45:18,981
Now, if you manage
to pull this off

923
00:45:18,983 --> 00:45:22,819
without a bullet in your head
and switch those pills,

924
00:45:22,821 --> 00:45:24,387
then switch 'em back.

925
00:45:25,989 --> 00:45:27,256
