You do this...

930
00:45:36,067 --> 00:45:38,067
Switch 'em back.

931
00:45:43,006 --> 00:45:44,741
So...

932
00:45:44,743 --> 00:45:46,142
You gonna
let us make this deal?

933
00:45:46,144 --> 00:45:47,777
You got the money?

934
00:45:50,180 --> 00:45:52,515
Good. [Sniffles]

935
00:45:52,517 --> 00:45:55,852
Now,
before we do this...

936
00:45:55,854 --> 00:45:58,354
I'm gonna need
one more thing from you.

937
00:46:02,192 --> 00:46:05,294
[Indistinct conversations]

938
00:46:05,296 --> 00:46:08,197
[Intercom beeps]

939
00:46:08,199 --> 00:46:10,099
Yes?

940
00:46:10,101 --> 00:46:12,201
Okay.

941
00:46:12,203 --> 00:46:14,904
Miss valco
will see you now.

942
00:46:14,906 --> 00:46:16,806
Oh.
Second door.

943
00:46:21,044 --> 00:46:24,847
[Breathes sharply]

944
00:46:24,849 --> 00:46:26,883
Hi there.
Come on in.

945
00:46:26,885 --> 00:46:28,217
Yeah. Hi.

946
00:46:28,219 --> 00:46:30,787
Uh, called
quite a few times

947
00:46:30,789 --> 00:46:33,856
about an issue
I'm trying to address.

948
00:46:33,858 --> 00:46:36,392
Do you have
your policy number?

949
00:46:36,394 --> 00:46:37,794
No. [Sighs]

950
00:46:37,796 --> 00:46:40,797
Can you just
look up my name?

951
00:46:40,799 --> 00:46:42,832
Mcgill?

952
00:46:45,903 --> 00:46:49,338
Charles mcgill
of Hamlin, Hamlin, mcgill?

953
00:46:49,340 --> 00:46:51,474
No,
that's my brother.

954
00:46:51,476 --> 00:46:52,875
Um...

955
00:46:52,877 --> 00:46:54,477
[Clears throat]
I'm Jimmy.

956
00:46:54,479 --> 00:46:55,878
James mcgill.

957
00:46:55,880 --> 00:46:58,147
Solo practitioner.

958
00:46:59,149 --> 00:47:00,817
Oh.
There you are.

959
00:47:00,819 --> 00:47:03,252
Looks like you're all paid up
through the year.

960
00:47:03,254 --> 00:47:05,121
That's sort of
the issue.

961
00:47:05,123 --> 00:47:06,355
Long story short,

962
00:47:06,357 --> 00:47:08,925
through a series
of unfortunate events,

963
00:47:08,927 --> 00:47:11,561
