has been suspended.

964
00:47:11,563 --> 00:47:13,196
Yes,
I see that here.

965
00:47:13,198 --> 00:47:14,430
Right.

966
00:47:14,432 --> 00:47:16,265
Well, I was hoping
I could get a refund

967
00:47:16,267 --> 00:47:18,100
for the time
that I won't be a lawyer.

968
00:47:18,102 --> 00:47:20,002
Now, that's only fair,
right?

969
00:47:20,004 --> 00:47:21,370
I'm sorry,
Mr. mcgill.

970
00:47:21,372 --> 00:47:23,105
It doesn't work
like that.

971
00:47:23,107 --> 00:47:26,976
