unused malpractice insurance.

972
00:47:26,978 --> 00:47:28,277
[Sighs]

973
00:47:28,279 --> 00:47:30,379
But it's a...
It's a lot of money for nothing.

974
00:47:30,381 --> 00:47:32,448
I understand
it seems that way,

975
00:47:32,450 --> 00:47:34,150
but if
one of your clients

976
00:47:34,152 --> 00:47:36,953
decides they want
to bring a suit against you,

977
00:47:36,955 --> 00:47:38,855
this continues
your coverage.

978
00:47:38,857 --> 00:47:40,056
[Snaps fingers]

979
00:47:40,058 --> 00:47:41,958
That's the thing.
My clients?

980
00:47:41,960 --> 00:47:43,292
