981
00:47:43,294 --> 00:47:46,462
And they would never bring
a suit against me.

982
00:47:46,464 --> 00:47:48,998
I'm [Chuckling]
Extremely lovable.

983
00:47:49,000 --> 00:47:50,867
I can see that.

984
00:47:50,869 --> 00:47:53,436
But it's company policy.

985
00:47:53,438 --> 00:47:55,304
[Snaps fingers]

986
00:47:55,306 --> 00:47:57,940
What about
we put the insurance on hold?

987
00:47:57,942 --> 00:48:00,142
And then, if someone were
to try to sue me...

988
00:48:00,144 --> 00:48:02,478
Which they won't...
Then we just, uh,

989
00:48:02,480 --> 00:48:05,147
[clicks tongue] Kick that ol'
policy back into gear?

990
00:48:05,149 --> 00:48:06,983
I understand
your situation.

991
00:48:06,985 --> 00:48:08,317
I do.

992
00:48:08,319 --> 00:48:09,986
But there are rules
preventing us

993
00:48:09,988 --> 00:48:12,221
