150%.

1002
00:48:42,185 --> 00:48:44,654
[Breathing sharply]

1003
00:48:44,656 --> 00:48:47,056
[Chuckling] God.

1004
00:48:47,058 --> 00:48:48,624
[Sniffling]

1005
00:48:48,626 --> 00:48:50,993
[Drawer closes]

1006
00:48:53,931 --> 00:48:54,997
Mr. mcgill?

1007
00:48:54,999 --> 00:48:58,267
[Sighs]

1008
00:48:58,269 --> 00:49:02,371
[Sniffles]

1009
00:49:02,373 --> 00:49:04,540
Oh.

1010
00:49:04,542 --> 00:49:05,942
I...

1011
00:49:05,944 --> 00:49:07,443
Mr. mcgill,
I'm sorry.

1012
00:49:07,445 --> 00:49:10,313
I wish we could help you,
but we just can't.

1013
00:49:10,315 --> 00:49:12,181
[Sniffles]

1014
00:49:12,183 --> 00:49:14,116
I'm sorry.

1015
00:49:15,719 --> 00:49:18,387
It's hard.

1016
00:49:18,389 --> 00:49:20,122
Very, very hard.

1017
00:49:20,124 --> 00:49:21,724
[Sniffles]

1018
00:49:21,726 --> 00:49:24,627
I'm just having
a rough time.

1019
00:49:24,629 --> 00:49:26,996
I just need
a break.

1020
00:49:26,998 --> 00:49:30,132
[Voice breaking]
Just one break.

1021
00:49:32,069 --> 00:49:37,073
And I know you... I know
you can't do anything, but...

1022
00:49:37,075 --> 00:49:38,474
[Crying]

1023
00:49:38,476 --> 00:49:42,745
I'm getting run out on
this community service and...

1024
00:49:42,747 --> 00:49:46,582
Getting ripped off
left and right, and...

1025
00:49:46,584 --> 00:49:48,484
My car won't start.

1026
00:49:48,486 --> 00:49:50,086
[Chuckles]

1027
00:49:50,088 --> 00:49:54,690
My gal is disappointed in me,
and my brother...

1028
00:49:54,692 --> 00:49:56,192
[Sniffles]

1029
00:49:58,195 --> 00:50:01,430
[Crying]
My brother is sick!

1030
00:50:01,432 --> 00:50:03,632
And he's alone.

1031
00:50:05,235 --> 00:50:08,004
I spent years
caring for him,

1032
00:50:08,006 --> 00:50:09,638
and now he hates me.

1033
00:50:09,640 --> 00:50:12,608
He's the only family
I got left,

1034
00:50:12,610 --> 00:50:14,477
and he hates me.

1035
00:50:14,479 --> 00:50:16,445
He hates my guts.

1036
00:50:16,447 --> 00:50:18,714
Is this
your brother, Charles?

1037
00:50:19,716 --> 00:50:21,217
Oh.
[Sniffles]

1038
00:50:21,219 --> 00:50:24,453
And I pretend not to care,
but he's my brother.

1039
00:50:24,455 --> 00:50:26,122
How can I not?

1040
00:50:26,124 --> 00:50:29,525
He's mentally ill.

1041
00:50:29,527 --> 00:50:32,294
He's... he's holed up in a house
with no electricity.

1042
00:50:32,296 --> 00:50:35,464
He's working
by the light of gas lanterns.

1043
00:50:35,466 --> 00:50:36,699
Wha...

1044
00:50:36,701 --> 00:50:39,135
He's making mistakes
with his clients.

1045
00:50:39,137 --> 00:50:42,638
He's mixin' up numbers
on important documents.

1046
00:50:42,640 --> 00:50:47,143
He... he... he had
a complete mental breakdown

1047
00:50:47,145 --> 00:50:48,744
at the bar hearing.

1048
00:50:48,746 --> 00:50:53,182
Your brother...
He had a breakdown in court?

1049
00:50:53,184 --> 00:50:55,785
It's in
the transcripts.

1050
00:50:55,787 --> 00:50:57,653
[Sobbing] God.

1051
00:50:57,655 --> 00:51:00,489
And I'm worried,
I'm just...

1052
