If he screws up
with one more big client...

1053
00:51:04,395 --> 00:51:07,296
It's just
gonna destroy him!

1054
00:51:08,698 --> 00:51:10,332
[Sniffles]

1055
00:51:10,334 --> 00:51:13,302
Oh, don't...
Don't write...

1056
00:51:13,304 --> 00:51:15,671
What are you writing?
No, don't write.

1057
00:51:15,673 --> 00:51:17,640
I-I didn't mean
